data.description: Looking for more space?  THIS is large living at its best. Located in the coveted Cimarron Sky subdivision of El Paso's west side, this 2927 sq ft property offers majestic mountain views. Newly renovated with brand new carpet and updated cabinets throughout. All stainless steel kitchen appliances are included as well as washer and dryer.  Versatile floor plan can easily change from a 6 bedroom home to a 5 bedroom with a maid's room/office to a 4 bedroom with a study and theater/media room.
